com.preemptive.annotation.instrumentation

Annotation Type OfflineModeSource


  • @Retention(value=CLASS)
@Target(value={TYPE,CONSTRUCTOR,METHOD})
public @interface OfflineModeSource
    Defines the source for the setting of off-line mode.

    See Also:
    ApplicationStart, OfflineMode, OfflineModeSupport, OfflineModeSupportSource, Specifying Sources and Actions, Dynamic Properties

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      java.lang.String value
      The source for the offline value.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      InjectionPoint where
      The location in the method where instrumentation will take place.
